{"word":"οὐτιδανός","slug":"οὐτιδανός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n76055\" key=\"ou)tidano/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">οὐτῐδᾰνός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ή</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, <sense id=\"n76055.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">of no account, worthless</tr_>, esp. with regard to strength or courage, in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> always of persons, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δειλὸς καὶ οὐ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:293\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.293</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">βέλος ἀνδρὸς ἀνάλκιδος, οὐτιδανοῖο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:390\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.390</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄφρων . . καὶ οὐ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:8:209\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.209</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀλίγος τε καὶ οὐ. καὶ ἄκικυς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:515\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.515</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐτιδανὸς βίην</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0023.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:144\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Opp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ H.\">H.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.144</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n76055.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Act.\">Act.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">reckless</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γᾶς δόσις οὐτιδανοῖς ἐν ῥοθίοις φορεῖται</foreign>, of a surging crowd, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg004.perseus-grc1:361\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">361</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.). (Prob. suffix <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-ανός</foreign>, and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Οὔτιδ</foreign>, earlier form of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὔτι</foreign> 'nothing', cf. Lat. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">quid</tr_>, Skt. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cid.</tr_>)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}